---
title: Chicken & Creamy Mushroom Sauce with Garlic Mashed Potatoes & Arugula Salad
description: The creamy mushroom sauce that cascades over juicy seared chicken makes this meal something special! (Okay, let’s not forget the velvety sour cream and garlic mashed potatoes, which might actually be why you’re here—no judgments!). Pile those creamy potatoes on the side, add a zingy, peppery arugula salad sprinkled with Parmesan for fresh crunch and pops of color, and you’re in for a sumptuously satisfying dinner.
